{"tid":646351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【富豪被玩謝】朱太逼降新加坡！香港私人飛機場有錢都冇位泊","createTime":"2018-04-29T03:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T08:23:54.000Z","uid":65328,"like":10,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec15cba1431570146b572f790e297f83a2fb874","tid":646351,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔起郵輪碼頭， 用返啟德機場專用黎做私人飛機機場會唔會更好， 方便世界各地有錢佬黎香港住/傾生意/投資， 釋放赤鱲角機場原本俾私人飛機升降既時間空間， 小型機飛廣州係咪重好過高鐵？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180428/584190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180428%2F584190&d=%2B9OPQEDzr2OMqe7q0QsGlP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=060ffe38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180428%2F584190&h=22746463\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180428/584190</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊度玩得富豪最謝？答案係私人飛機場！想book time slot 起飛或降落要預早booking,但又唔擔保有冇位噃，搞到啲有部私人飛機嘅闊佬好冇瘾！抛個身出嚟投訴又冇人可憐。講到私人飛機場香港同新加坡已冇得揮，坡佬係原本屬軍事基地的Seletar舊機場設立私人飛機場，多家世界級飛機製造商如Bombardier，Airbus等等都設立基地，直頭有個320公頃Aerospace Park供有錢佬泊飛機。喜歡坐住部私人飛機四出揾商機兼與友人出埠聯誼嘅金利豐老闆朱太，早排因為香港冇time slot俾佢，被逼降落新加坡留係當地玩兩日。"},{"pid":"03104a65e7fb5c861c7abb97eff79d8bed0c7060","tid":646351,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"澳門囉，第日有港豬噢"},{"pid":"f924d6bbdebc982d65f93bd8c71d9aa216f8e9ec","tid":646351,"uid":20227,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:27:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ed10d9e5809f08b604726744af3f0d1c7534a4f","tid":646351,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03104a65e7fb5c861c7abb97eff79d8bed0c7060","tid":646351,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"澳門囉，第日有港豬噢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018